      "writtenOn": "2020-11-23T17:30:39Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "In this case IMO it\u0027s a little confusing to use the term patchset to mean revision number. My understanding before was that:\n - patchset and revision are synonyms, and\n - patchset number and revision number are synonyms.\n\nGerrit tends to prefer \"revision\" internally. Right? So I\u0027d replace \"patchset\" with \"patchset number\" or even \"revision number\".",
